Pattern Recognition
Prefix Minimum Pattern

Many questions ask:

Current Value - Best Previous Value

Use:

bestPrevious = min(bestPrevious, current)

Examples:

LeetCode 121 (Best Time to Buy and Sell Stock)
Maximum Difference Between Increasing Elements
Best Sightseeing Pair (variation)
